OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FSome low cloud around this
OL,6,Fmorning, possibly some mist and fog
OL,7,Fpatches too, eventually clearing to a
OL,8,Fbright day. Thicker cloud will
OL,9,Feventually push in from the northwest
OL,10,Flater, with some spots of drizzle.
OL,11,FFeeling Spring-like with above average
OL,12,Ftemperatures.
OL,13,
OL,14,CTonight:FTurning increasingly cloudy
OL,15,Fovernight with some rain and drizzle.
OL,16,FTurning breezier by the morning too. A
OL,17,Fmild night to come.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
